===亚美尼亚撤军===
11月13日起<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://oc-media.org/live-updates-some-armenian-residents-of-kalbajar-burn-homes/ |title=Live updates: Some Armenian residents of Kalbajar burn homes |date=2020-11-13 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=OC Media |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113094413/https://oc-media.org/live-updates-some-armenian-residents-of-kalbajar-burn-homes/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[克尔巴贾尔区|克尔巴贾尔区]]的亚美尼亚人开始烧掉自己的家，回到亚美尼亚，避免被阿塞拜疆人占用<ref>{{Cite web |first=Anelise |last=Borges |url=https://www.euronews.com/2020/11/14/nagorno-karabakh-ethnic-armenians-set-fire-to-their-homes-rather-than-hand-them-to-azerbai |title=Nagorno-Karabakh: Ethnic Armenians set fire to their homes rather than hand them to Azerbaijan |date=2020-11-14 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Euronews |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114100002/https://www.euronews.com/2020/11/14/nagorno-karabakh-ethnic-armenians-set-fire-to-their-homes-rather-than-hand-them-to-azerbai |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.startribunemag.com/kalbajar-residents-burn-homes-before-azerbaijan-handover/ |title=Kalbajar residents burn houses earlier than Azerbaijan handover |date=2020-11-15 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Star Tribune |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202150947/https://www.startribunemag.com/kalbajar-residents-burn-homes-before-azerbaijan-handover/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/world-news/armenians-residents-in-kalbajar-burn-their-homes-before-azerbaijan-handover/videoshow/79234016.cms |title=Nagorno-Karabakh: Villagers burn their homes ahead of peace deal |date=2020-11-15 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Economic Times |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116104955/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/world-news/armenians-residents-in-kalbajar-burn-their-homes-before-azerbaijan-handover/videoshow/79234016.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该区是第一次纳卡战争前曾是阿塞拜疆居民最多的地区，战后由亚美尼亚人居住<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rferl.org/a/armenia-to-begin-handing-over-territory-to-azerbaijan-under-terms-of-truce/30950886.html |title=Azerbaijan Extends Deadline For Armenia To Withdraw From Key District Under Karabakh Truce |date=2020-11-15 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115081119/https://www.rferl.org/a/armenia-to-begin-handing-over-territory-to-azerbaijan-under-terms-of-truce/30950886.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20201113-armenians-flee-homes-as-azerbaijan-takeover-looms |title=Armenians flee homes as Azerbaijan takeover looms |date=2020-11-13 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=France24 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113223739/https://www.france24.com/en/live-news/20201113-armenians-flee-homes-as-azerbaijan-takeover-looms |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |first=Filippo |last=Rossi |url=https://www.letemps.ch/monde/armeniens-karvachar-route-lexode |title=Les Arméniens du Karvachar sur la route de l’exode |date=2020-11-15 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Le Temps |language=fr |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115153656/https://www.letemps.ch/monde/armeniens-karvachar-route-lexode |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部分亚美尼亚人还带上了罹难亲属的遗体<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/14/nagorno-karabakh-villagers-burn-their-homes-ahead-of-peace-deal |title=Armenians residents in Kalbajar burn their homes before Azerbaijan handover |date=2020-11-14 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=The Guardian |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114185915/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/14/nagorno-karabakh-villagers-burn-their-homes-ahead-of-peace-deal |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也有人用卡车搬走全部家当<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-armenia-azerbaijan-village-idUSKBN27U0FQ |title=Armenians set fire to homes before handing village over to Azerbaijan |date=2020-11-14 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Reuters |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114152058/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-armenia-azerbaijan-village-idUSKBN27U0FQ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。据法新社报道，Charektar村至少有六间民房被烧<ref>{{Cite web |first=Hervé |last=Bar |url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/11/15/azerbaijan-extends-armenian-pullout-deadline-from-disputed-area-a72048 |title=Azerbaijan Extends Armenian Pullout Deadline From Disputed Area |date=2020-11-15 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=The Moscow Times |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115140525/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/11/15/azerbaijan-extends-armenian-pullout-deadline-from-disputed-area-a72048 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月15日，应亚美尼亚要求，阿塞拜疆将克尔巴贾尔区的亚美尼亚人完全撤离的截止时间延后10日至11月25日。阿塞拜疆总统办公室表示，他们是考虑到恶劣的天气及前往亚美尼亚的道路只有一条，而做出的决定<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/11/15/armenia-cedes-disputed-land-to-azerbaijan-after-peace-deal |title=Azerbaijan extends Armenian pullout deadline from Kalbajar |date=2020-11-15 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Al Jazeera |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115111848/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/11/15/armenia-cedes-disputed-land-to-azerbaijan-after-peace-deal |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿塞拜疆当局谴责平民和复员士兵离开当地时[[焦土政策|烧掉房屋]]，称这是“生态恐怖袭击”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/world/asia/ecological-terror-azerbaijan-delays-takeover-denounces-fleeing-armenians-20201116-p56eu6.html?ref=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_source=rss_feed |title='Ecological terror': Azerbaijan delays takeover, Armenians torch homes |date=2020-11-15 |access-date=2020-11-15 |work=Brisbane Times |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202151017/https://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/world/asia/ecological-terror-azerbaijan-delays-takeover-denounces-fleeing-armenians-20201116-p56eu6.html?ref=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_source=rss_feed |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thewire.in/world/ethnic-armenians-set-fire-to-homes-before-handing-over-village-to-azerbaijan|title=Ethnic Armenians Set Fire to Homes Before Handing Over Village to Azerbaijan|date=2020-11-15|access-date=2020-11-17|work=Reuters|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115165054/https://thewire.in/world/ethnic-armenians-set-fire-to-homes-before-handing-over-village-to-azerbaijan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===俄国维和部队进驻===
早在2020年11月10日，俄罗斯按照协议组建的部队便已进入纳卡地区<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/armenia-azerbaijan/russian-peacekeepers-deploy-to-nagorno-karabakh-after-ceasefire-deal-idUSKBN27Q11R |title=Russian peacekeepers deploy to Nagorno-Karabakh after ceasefire |work=Reuters |date=2020-11-10 |access-date=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123101954/https://www.reuters.com/article/armenia-azerbaijan/russian-peacekeepers-deploy-to-nagorno-karabakh-after-ceasefire-deal-idUSKBN27Q11R |dead-url=no }}</ref>。协议签订前，俄军便空降至亚美尼亚<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.svoboda.org/a/30956980.html|title="РФ могла оказывать поддержку только с территории Ирана"|publisher=Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty|date=2020-11-18|language=ru|accessdate=2020-11-30|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127035442/https://www.svoboda.org/a/30956980.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到12日，主要由{{le|第15独立机动步枪旅|15th Separate Motor Rifle Brigade}}组成的俄军部队进驻斯捷潘纳克特，在当地部署观察哨<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://tass.com/world/1223203 |title=Russian peacekeepers enter Stepanakert |work=TASS |date=2020-11-12 |access-date=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118112247/https://tass.com/world/1223203 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2022年3月26日，俄罗斯国防部指责阿塞拜疆军队进入了纳卡地区俄维和部队的负责区域并设置了观察哨，违反俄阿亚三方签署的联合声明。阿塞拜疆否認俄罗斯国防部的指控。<ref>{{cite news |title=俄称阿塞拜疆军队进入纳卡地区违反三方声明 阿方对此表示否认 |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/47MChBb72xX |accessdate=2022-03-27 |archive-date=2022-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220418173224/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/47MChBb72xX }}</ref>

===土耳其军队的角色===
俄罗斯和土耳其国防部长签订合作备忘录，计划在阿塞拜疆成立俄罗斯-土耳其联合监察中心<ref name="aljazseeks">{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/11/16/turkey-seeks-approval-to-deploy-peacekeepers-in-azerbaijan|title=Turkey seeks approval to deploy peacekeepers in Azerbaijan|work=Al Jazeera|date=2020-11-16|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123095759/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/11/16/turkey-seeks-approval-to-deploy-peacekeepers-in-azerbaijan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而俄方坚持土耳其的参与会限制监察中心在阿塞拜疆领土远程行动的能力，要求土耳其维和部队不进入纳卡地区<ref name="aljazseeks" /><ref name="tassnoturks">{{Cite web |url=https://tass.com/politics/1222931 |title=No Turkish peacekeepers to be sent to Nagorno-Karabakh — Lavrov |work=TASS |date=2020-11-12 |access-date=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128141811/https://tass.com/politics/1222931 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

